;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;">Sam Gregory</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">英国UK</strong></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">鼓/音乐制作/乐队班 Drum/Music Production/Band Class</p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/dwTCbxYiaHQ2Cvan2QNS9H5emV26urF8DfBWgCOsJ2KHQ4RPpcbaaSShsvtyEaMe18zU4Q1vpg8GZicU7MB4jichg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.6660412757973734" data-w="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 533px;"/><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Sam Gregory 从15岁年开始学鼓，自此，鼓就是他的声音，乐队就是他的生命。他热爱金属，爵士、Hip Hop,&nbsp;雷鬼，古典乐等不同类型的音乐文化。在英国创办知名乐队Downslide.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">他在The University of Huddersfield完成流行音乐学位后，又在谢菲尔德大学研读，并在摇滚音乐学院任教，为不同年龄的学生开办乐队工作坊及传递乐队文化与乐趣。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Sam Gregory started playing the drums at the age of 15. He found his voice in hitting the drums, and that started his life playing in bands. He particularly loves Metal, Drum n Bass, Jazz, Hip Hop, Reggae, and Classical music. He studied music at the Sheffield College and gained a BA hons Popular Music at The University of Huddersfield. He also formed theUK band, Downslide.</p></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">He taught drums to students of different ages at The Wreck Room and School of Rock Music School, using the Trinity Rock School and London College of Music curricula. He ran band workshops, which were designed to promote interest with the younger ages, and develop skills and band communication with the older ages.He has&nbsp; appeared on recordings released worldwide on Rising Records, Sony Italy and Zhuluhefeng. Sam has gained a wealth of performance experience having toured Europe and China with the bands, Downslide, Cause of Denial, Blue Magpie and TMOOS.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="87417" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;"><img data-id="87417" title="音符" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/cZV2hRpuAPiaJQXWGyC9wrUzIicibgXayrgibTYarT3A1yzttbtaO0JlV21wMqroGYT3QtPq2C7HMYsvicSB2p7dTBg/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.45454545454545453" data-w="22" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;">Giulio Perinello</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">意大利Italy</strong></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">吉他/贝斯/音乐制作/乐队班 Guitar/Bass Guitar/Music Production/Band Class</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/dwTCbxYiaHQ0TK28aIR9ht6QlG2rxRA3pRoTDrHXU03blGh76YVrOT2ETIVic2ib8PtgsEdVCYuwowxDVicW7WzRYQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 533px;"/><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Guilio Perinello 来自意大利,&nbsp;幼时在意大利音乐学院学习大管,之后在多支乐队做贝斯手。2010年毕业于意大利著名的Saluzzo音乐学院，专业是互动音乐制作与多媒体艺术。之后，他就开始了他的音乐制作人与作曲生涯，并与多位西班牙与国际艺术家合作。他在智利的Conde Duque唱片公司发表了他的House音乐，在马德里、墨西哥和Ibiza做DJ。他在演出中经常探索计算机音乐的多种可能性，并在西班牙、伦敦、葡萄牙的各大艺术节演奏吉他和贝斯。2013年起，他在西班牙重要机构如马德里欧洲设计学院发展并教授电子音乐课程。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Giulio Perinello is from the North of Italy. His relationship with music began in early childhood, studying bassoon at the Conservatory and later playing electric bass with several bands.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">In 2010, he graduated from the renowned APM institute of Saluzzo (Italy) with a degree in &quot;Interactive Music Production for Digital Arts.&quot;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Since then he has been expanding his career in Madrid, working as producer and composer in collaboration with several Spanish and international artists.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">He released house tracks with Conde Duque record label from Chile, promoting his music as DJ in Madrid, Mexico and Ibiza parties.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Constantly exploring new ways to integrate the computer as an instrument in the live shows, he has been playing guitar and bass in multimedia shows in Spain, London and Portugal festivals with his Umami Connection live cinema project.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">In 2013 he started his activity as computer music teacher, developing successfully courses in important institutions such as European Design Institute of Madrid, teaching complete programs about digital music creation.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Now in Shanghai he is working as DJ in various clubs and has started a new live project in collaboration with Chinese musicians, mixing electronic, rock and traditional influences.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="87417" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;"><img data-id="87417" title="音符" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/cZV2hRpuAPiaJQXWGyC9wrUzIicibgXayrgibTYarT3A1yzttbtaO0JlV21wMqroGYT3QtPq2C7HMYsvicSB2p7dTBg/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.45454545454545453" data-w="22" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><section class="135editor" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;">叶晔Yeye</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">中国&nbsp;China</strong></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">键盘/乐队班 Piano/Band Class</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/dwTCbxYiaHQ2Cvan2QNS9H5emV26urF8DjMfLPlRqdAr6wQLXfK13s8zNmib641BaISUbqvdfRXhSrdnS88qfJEQ/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.6885553470919324" data-w="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 533px;"/><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">从五岁开始学习钢琴，2009年毕业于上海音乐学院；2011至2013年在巴塞罗那&nbsp;Taller De Musics&nbsp;音乐学校、里西奥音乐学院研读拉丁与弗拉门戈音乐的钢琴演奏；目前在上海与其他乐队进行跨界演出。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Ye Ye began studying piano when he was 5 years old. He graduated from the Shanghai Music Conservatory in 2009. He then decided to continue his studies in Barcelona, taking classes in Latin and Flamenco piano at the Taller de Musics Modern Music School and Liceu Conservatory from 2011 to 2013.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="87417" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;"><img data-id="87417" title="音符" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/cZV2hRpuAPiaJQXWGyC9wrUzIicibgXayrgibTYarT3A1yzttbtaO0JlV21wMqroGYT3QtPq2C7HMYsvicSB2p7dTBg/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.45454545454545453" data-w="22" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><section class="135editor" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;">James Hogan</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">爱尔兰 Ireland</strong></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">吉他/贝斯/乐队班 Guitar/Band Class</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/dwTCbxYiaHQ2Cvan2QNS9H5emV26urF8DDSQswticW5zG840qSDjP04XibicYicXbae0152hQUs2eu6sVOCTia9xokKA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.6660412757973734" data-w="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 533px;"/><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">James Hogan出生在都柏林，他父亲是爱尔兰七八十年代现代音乐界领军人物，自小对音乐耳濡目染。他10岁在全国广播电视转播的合唱队中演出，并学习小提琴、音乐理论和作曲。十四岁开始学习吉他，大学作为贝斯手组乐队曾获爱尔兰乐队比赛决赛奖项，之后又在伦敦成立了新乐队Pilot Light。James在4年前来到中国，在多支乐队中担任吉他贝斯手，包括摇滚、爵士、hip－hop和布鲁斯等。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">James Hogan was born in Dublin, Ireland to&nbsp;a musical family. His father was a lead guitarist in modern music of the 70’s and 80’s. James was 10 years old when he featured on a televised chorus performance hosted by NBC. At the time, he was learning violin, music theory and composition. He learned to play the guitar at 14 years old. He was an Irish Band Competition finalist and has formed several bands, including Pilot Light. James came to China 4 years ago and is currently a guitarist for several bands. He is familiar with a diverse range of music genres, including rock, jazz, hip-hop and blues.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="87417" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;"><img data-id="87417" title="音符" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/cZV2hRpuAPiaJQXWGyC9wrUzIicibgXayrgibTYarT3A1yzttbtaO0JlV21wMqroGYT3QtPq2C7HMYsvicSB2p7dTBg/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.45454545454545453" data-w="22" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><section class="135editor" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;">刘炜 Liu Wei</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">中国 China</strong></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">贝司/吉他/乐队班 Guitar/Bass Guitar/Band Class</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/dwTCbxYiaHQ2Cvan2QNS9H5emV26urF8DETSPOK3WNHHBiaf3icYSaXYn0Rd0aXY6XiahNmRGDesPg5DzFr62OAiaZw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.7504690431519699" data-w="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 533px;"/><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Bass（贝司）演奏家刘炜活跃于古典和爵士及流行音乐领域。现任上海馨田交响乐团经理，行政总监。01年进入上海广播交响乐团（现上海爱乐乐团）工作，历年来与众多中外著名指挥家，演奏家等音乐家和团体合作在国内及出访亚洲，欧洲，美洲等国演出。同时担任上海节日交响乐团，上海歌剧院艺术团乐团，Shanghai Baroque chamber orchestra，上海音韵室内乐团，上海轻音乐团贝司首席。并作为客席演奏家受邀于上海交响乐团。在爵士乐领域，参演了英国伦敦西区与百老汇中国巡演，英国GWB公司的《极致百老汇》，并与外籍音乐家Spencer ，IGARASHI和NAKANO等人组建了“刘炜爵士四重奏”组合。参加历年北京国际音乐节，上海国际艺术节，上海国际爵士音乐节等演出活动。</p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Bass Guitarist, Liu Wei, is active in Classical, Jazz and Pop music. He is the Chairman of Shanghai Xin Tian Symphony Orchestra manager and administrative director. In 2001, Liu Wei entered the Shanghai Broadcasting Symphony Orchestra, now known as the Shanghai Philharmonic Orchestra. He has worked over the years with many Chinese and foreign famous conductors, musicians and other performers and groups to cooperate in the country&#39;s domestic music culture. In addition, he has visited various countries in Asia, Europe, America to participate in performances. Liu Wei has also been a member of Shanghai Opera Troupe Orchestra, Shanghai Baroque Chamber Orchestra, Shanghai Phonology Chamber Orchestra, and served as the Bass Chief for Shanghai Light Music Group. In the field of Jazz music, he has appeared in London&#39;s West End and Broadway (while touring China), Britain GWB&#39;s &quot;Ultimate Broadway&quot; and with foreign musicians, like Spencer, IGARASHI and NAKANO, to form a jazz quartet combination. Over the years, he has attended Beijing International Music Festival, Shanghai International Arts Festival, Shanghai International Jazz Festival performances.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p></section><p class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="87417" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;"><img data-id="87417" title="音符" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/cZV2hRpuAPiaJQXWGyC9wrUzIicibgXayrgibTYarT3A1yzttbtaO0JlV21wMqroGYT3QtPq2C7HMYsvicSB2p7dTBg/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.45454545454545453" data-w="22" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><section class="135editor" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;">Krystal Lewis</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">美国 the United States&nbsp;</strong></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">唱歌/乐队班 Vocal/Band Class</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/dwTCbxYiaHQ0rApV1vGGFmdI7S0y5bNZGWWkH0Db6pqmHThODSedQNDrsGIt1H7Wwicicco2oU93VIlDRuecIKbow/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.7504690431519699" data-w="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 533px;"/><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Krystal Lewis来自美国德克萨斯中部。青少年时期她为当地教堂唱歌并演奏钢琴。她参加过地区级和国家级的团体及个人比赛，作为格罗斯贝克学区乐队的成员，她在乐队中演奏单簧管和低音单簧管长达7年。当她开始学习声乐课程时，她发现了自己对唱歌的热爱。这一改变为她之后的登台表演打开了大门。2015年7月，Krystal从塔尔顿州立大学毕业后便移居上海。她目前在上海作为各类艺术家做背景演唱，同时进行教学和表演，她选择的流派是新灵魂乐和R&amp;B蓝调音乐。带着对人们和对音乐的热爱，她十分乐于指导学生们用他们的声音作为道具去掌控和表达自己。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Krystal Lewis comes from the Central Texas in the US. As an adolescent, she took part in singing and playing piano for her local church. Competing in both regional and state competitions for solos and ensembles, she was a member of the band for the Groesbeck School District for 7 years as a clarinet and bass clarinet player. She discovered her love for singing when she traded her piano lessons for vocal training. This change opened doors for her to perform in many community events. Krystal moved to Shanghai in July of 2015 after graduation from Tarleton State University. Though she now teaches and performs as a backup vocalist for various artists in Shanghai, her genres of choice are Neo-Soul and R&amp;B. With both her love for people and music, she enjoys guiding her students to master and express themselves with their vocal instruments.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="87417" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;"><img data-id="87417" title="音符" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/cZV2hRpuAPiaJQXWGyC9wrUzIicibgXayrgibTYarT3A1yzttbtaO0JlV21wMqroGYT3QtPq2C7HMYsvicSB2p7dTBg/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.45454545454545453" data-w="22" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;">Ben Misterka</span></strong></span></section><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;">美国 the United States &nbsp;</span></strong><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">吉他\\贝斯\\鼓\\键盘</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/dwTCbxYiaHQ2Cvan2QNS9H5emV26urF8DZh50sAcDCrRJlV8MtacknPa5FeHz08LOaqwXdia2zHnJBVok0A6rWEA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.1313320825515947" data-w="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 533px;"/><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Ben Misterka,毕业于美国弗吉尼亚联邦大学爵士专业，是一名出色的吉他手、作曲家、音乐教练；擅长爵士、摇滚、古典、蓝调等不同音乐风格；足迹遍布中国、日本、美国等地的大型音乐节；合作过的艺人包括有：窦靖童、羽泉、回到蒙古、Anhayla、Kimberly Nichole、Joye B. Moore等等。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">2010-2012年亮相 Richmond International Jazz Festival；2014年进行了世界巡回演出；2015年他先与上海巴罗克室内乐团合作，在上海音乐厅演出古典吉他；而后又在美国著名爵士乐歌手CherryBrown合奏。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Ben Misterka is a American guitarist, composer, and music educator. A versatile musican, Misterka&#39;s travels have allowed him to be influenced by music from around the world.&nbsp; Relocating to Shanghai, China in 2012, he continues to write, perform, and record the music that he loves. &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Misterka has toured through China, Japan, and the USA, playing with many acclaimed artists, including the unique singer/songwriter Leah Dou (窦靖童) and pop/rock mainstays Yu Quan (羽泉), RTM(Return to Mongolia), Anhayla, Kimberly Nichole, Joye B. Moore and many others. &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Notable performances include; Richmond International Jazz Festival, Shanghai JZ Festival in 2013 with New Grasslands, and 2015 with RTM, Ordos World Music Festival- Inner Mongolia and many others.&nbsp; He has performed at several of the major venues and festivals in Shanghai and around China, including the Mercedes-Benz Mixing Room, Booshkabash, Shanghai World Music festival and many more.&nbsp; In 2014 he held a 2-month residency at “House of Blues and Jazz” in Shanghai, and later that year was invited to perform on classical guitar with the Shanghai Baroque Chamber Orchestra at the Shanghai Concert Hall.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Misterka has played for numerous recording sessions for an array of styles.&nbsp; He has released 2 self produced records with New Grasslands, and will soon debut an EP of his solo material. &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="87417" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;"><img data-id="87417" title="音符" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/cZV2hRpuAPiaJQXWGyC9wrUzIicibgXayrgibTYarT3A1yzttbtaO0JlV21wMqroGYT3QtPq2C7HMYsvicSB2p7dTBg/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.45454545454545453" data-w="22" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><section class="135editor" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;">蔡志铮 Cai Zhizheng</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 25.6px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">中国 China</strong></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">吉他/贝斯/乐队班 Guitar/Band Class</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/dwTCbxYiaHQ2Cvan2QNS9H5emV26urF8Dpy66ZpaNicc1tAhXtH1DTtV5bBts2qBx4zGgiclgyp5CyjFnNGYEibsQA/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.9024390243902439" data-w="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 533px;"/><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">先毕业于北京迷笛音乐学校，后毕业于中央音乐学院，现主要从事音乐剧现场伴奏、录制、创作，有10年以上丰富教学经验；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">撰写《吉他演奏就是这么简单》教材；主要参演、创作、录制的作品有：《妈妈咪呀》、《杜拉拉》、《番茄不简单》、《撒娇女王》、《资本•论》、《你是我的孤独》、《仲夏》、《spin》、《我和春天有个约会》、《寻找初恋》、《苏州河》、《香水》、《南京攻略》、《www.com》、《红绿变换曲》等三十几部作品。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">Cai Zhipeng graduated from the Beijing Midi School of Music and the Central Conservatory of Music. He is mainly engaged in live music accompaniment, recording, and writing. He has over 10 years of teaching experience. Cai Zhipeng has written “Guitar Playing Is As Simple As” teaching material. He has composed pieces for about 30 films and musicals. His recorded works include Mamma Mia, Story of Du LaLa, Simple Tomato, Spoiled Queen, Capital On, You Are My Loneliness, Midsummer, Spin, I Have a Date With Spring, Looking for Love, and Suzhou River.&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="87417" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;"><img data-id="87417" title="音符" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/cZV2hRpuAPiaJQXWGyC9wrUzIicibgXayrgibTYarT3A1yzttbtaO0JlV21wMqroGYT3QtPq2C7HMYsvicSB2p7dTBg/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.45454545454545453" data-w="22" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(&quot;http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif&quot;);"></section></section><p><br/></p>', '明星教师', '', '/uploads/201607268232Epui1mIYKL.jpg', '', 'single', '2016-07-26 18:26:45');
INSERT INTO `materials` (`id`, `keywords`, `content`, `title`, `source_url`, `coverurl`, `summary`, `type`, `createtime`) VALUES
(2, '课程', '<section label="Powered by 135editor.com" style="font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="86352" style="border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 5px auto; width: 50%; box-sizing: border-box;" class="layout" data-width="50%"><section style="height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="height: 0.6em; width: 0.6em; float: left; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-left-width: 1px; border-left-style: solid; border-top-left-radius: 50%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="height: 0.6em; width: 0.6em; float: right; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-top-right-radius: 50%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="margin: -0.8em 0.1em -0.8em 0.2em; padding: 0.8em; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text">精品课程</p></section></section><section style="height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="height: 0.6em; width: 0.6em; float: left; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-left-width: 1px; border-left-style: solid; border-bottom-left-radius: 50%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="height: 0.6em; width: 0.6em; float: right; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-right-radius: 50%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">精品课程</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Rolling Music提供立体化创意课程和线上线下完整教学体系：统一教案精确到分，阶梯学习逐级强化，实现精准化教学；在线下载音视频库和教学文件，教师实时掌握学员学习动态，实现成效化学习；舞台表演、社会实践辅助教学，实现立体化训练；线上教务系统查询课程、完成作业、师生评定，实现信息化管理。</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">Courses</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Rolling Music operates with a three-dimensional, creative course curriculum. Complete with in-school and online instruction, we present comprehensive lesson plans with ordered objectives to strengthen achievement and understanding. The online component allows students to download audio and video files, and direct instruction provided by the teacher. With course objective completion, students can earn opportunity to participate in teacher-aided events and live stage performances.</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">1. 器乐班</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">包含吉他、贝司、钢琴、架子鼓、尤克里里、唱歌等课程，教授不同音乐风格，乐器技法与即兴创作，原创课程与考级辅导（ROCKSCHOOL/英皇/迷笛考级）双线教学。钢琴适合4岁以上儿童及成年人，其他乐器适合7岁以上儿童及成年人。</p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">Instrument Classes</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Comprising of Guitar, Bass Guitar, Piano, Drums, Ukulele, Vocal, and other courses to come, RM utilizes improvisation and a number of techniques along with original curriculum to teach lessons. We look at RockSchool, Letters and Midi for a dual-grading criteria. Piano courses are offered to children of 4 years and older, as well as adults. Other courses are provided for children of&nbsp; 7 years and older as well as adults.</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">2. 乐队合奏班</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">乐队班致力于培养学员的团队合作意识，社交能力和问题处理能力。课程将教授如何与乐队成员合作演奏，充分锻炼学员的应变能力、即兴演奏能力和舞台技巧。适合有器乐基础的学员，也可为整支乐队提供创作和表演辅导。</p><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">2.</span></p><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">Get in a Band and Play a Show</span></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Band Class specializes in demonstrating skills sets for teamwork, communication, and problem solving. Students are taught how to cooperate with band members for practicing both class exercises and band material, improvisation numbers, and stage performances. This training provides consultation for individual instruments in its contribution to creativity and performances of the entire band. &nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">3. 电脑音乐制作班</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">教授软件功能学习与运用、录音混音和电子音乐创作，适合有乐理基础、器乐基础且会使用电脑的12岁以上青少年及成年人。</p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">3. Music Production</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Music Production classes combine electronic recording and mixing music with professional software. This course is provided on both music theory and instrument-based production. Music Production is available for individuals of age 12 years and older.&nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">4. 音乐理论班</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">教授乐理基础，结合流行音乐史和不同音乐风格的器乐应用，适合7岁以上儿童和成人。</p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">4. Music Theory</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Music Theory classes provide students with history of popular music styles and instrumental applications of a diverse number of genres. This course is available for children of 7 years and older, as well as adults.&nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">5. 冬夏令营</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">每年寒暑推出“Let&#39;s Start A Band小小乐队夏令营”，了解不同音乐风格，器乐演奏方法及词曲创作，通过组乐队的形式帮助学员找到同好者，形成音乐社交圈，培养学员的团队意识和社交能力，并于闭营时完成乐队表演。适合7岁以上儿童及成人，有无器乐基础均可。</p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">Winter /Summer Camp</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Annually, RM launches seasonal ‘Let’s Start A Band’ mini-band camps of different music styles. Teachers present instrumental methods and songwriting techniques to assist students discover personal interests, cultivate a sense of community among peers, and develop social skills. At the close of each camp session, bands will participate in performances.&nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">课程费用</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center;"><br/></p><section class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="86265" style="border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><h2 class="135brush layout" data-brushtype="text" style="white-space: normal; font-size: 16px; margin: 10px auto; padding: 10px; width: 100%; max-width: 100%; border-top-width: 3px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36) rgb(255, 129, 36) rgb(229, 229, 229); border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); text-align: center;" data-width="100%"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;">A套餐</span></h2></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">一对一：19800元 （包括48节课或合奏排练＋30小时自主练习＋考级辅导或完整曲目练习＋演出机会，65周内使用）</p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">一对多（3-6人）：11800元（包括48节课或合奏排练＋考级辅导或完整曲目练习＋演出机会，65周内使用 ）</p><section class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="86265" style="border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><h2 class="135brush layout" data-brushtype="text" style="white-space: normal; font-size: 16px; margin: 10px auto; padding: 10px; width: 100%; max-width: 100%; border-top-width: 3px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36) rgb(255, 129, 36) rgb(229, 229, 229); border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); text-align: center;" data-width="100%"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;">B套餐</span></h2></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">一对一：7700元（包括16节课或合奏排练＋10小时自主练习＋考级辅导或完整曲目练习，26周内使用）</p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">一对多（6人以内）：4500元（包括16节课考级辅导或完整曲目练习＋考级辅导或完整曲目练习，26周内使用）</p><section class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="86265" style="border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><h2 class="135brush layout" data-brushtype="text" style="white-space: normal; font-size: 16px; margin: 10px auto; padding: 10px; width: 100%; max-width: 100%; border-top-width: 3px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36) rgb(255, 129, 36) rgb(229, 229, 229); border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); text-align: center;" data-width="100%"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;">夏令营</span></h2></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center;">3800元/期/人</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="135editor" style="position: static; border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(255, 129, 36)"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 8px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF8124;">Course Fees</span></p></section></section></section></section><section class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="86265" style="border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><h2 class="135brush layout" data-brushtype="text" style="white-space: normal; font-size: 16px; margin: 10px auto; padding: 10px; width: 100%; max-width: 100%; border-top-width: 3px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36) rgb(255, 129, 36) rgb(229, 229, 229); border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); text-align: center;" data-width="100%">Package A</h2></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">1-to-1: 19,800rmb</p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">(includes 48 lessons + 30hours ofindividual practice + a choice of graded exam certification or graded performance)</p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">The opportunity to perform at an eventcan be achieved during 65 weeks</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Group (3-6 people): 11,800rmb&nbsp;</p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">(includes 48 lesson + a choice of graded exam certification or graded performance)</p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">The opportunity to perform at an&nbsp; event can be achieved during 65 weeks</p><section class="135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="86265" style="border: 0px none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><h2 class="135brush layout" data-brushtype="text" style="white-space: normal; font-size: 16px; margin: 10px auto; padding: 10px; width: 100%; max-width: 100%; border-top-width: 3px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36) rgb(255, 129, 36) rgb(229, 229, 229); border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); text-align: center;" data-width="100%"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;">Package B</span></h2></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section class="135title" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></section><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">1-to-1: 7,700rmb</p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">(includes 16 lessons + 10 hours of individual practice +a choice of graded exam certification or graded performancewithin 26 weeks)</p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Group (6 persons or less): 4,500rmb&nbsp;</p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">(includes 16 lessons + 10 hours of individual practice +a choice of graded exam certification or graded performancewithin 26 weeks)</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section style="-webkit-border-image:url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);"></section></section><p><br/></p>', '精品课程', '', '/uploads/201607266357MNF8tTR5Wj.gif', '', 'single', '2016-07-26 18:34:06'),
(3, '关于', '<section style="font-family: 微软雅黑;" label="Powered by 135editor.com"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; box-sizing: border-box;" class="135editor" data-id="86448" data-tools="135编辑器"><section style="margin-top: 1em; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"><section style="text-align: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: 0.6em; font-size: 4em; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;"><em class="135brush" data-brushtype="text">A</em></section></section><section style="color: inherit; margin-left: 0.2em; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="line-height: 1.4; white-space: normal;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text">BOUT &nbsp;Rolling Music</p><p style="line-height: 1.4; font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text">关于我们</p></section></section><section style="color: inherit; margin-top: -1em; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: -5px; border-top-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); border-right-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: -6px -6px 0px; padding: 3px; border-radius: 100%; width: 14px; height: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1; float: right; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"><section style="border-radius: 50%; width: 8px; height: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(33, 33, 34);"></section></section><section style="padding: 10px 15px 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;" class="135brush" data-style="font-size: 14px;line-height:1.5em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><p style="color: inherit; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 14px;">Rolling Music（RM） 是一个集音乐教育和演出为一体的音乐机构，由国内大型音乐节创办人及富有教育经验的团队策划，一流的专业乐手任教，致力于推广现代音乐文化，开发及教授音 乐理论、欣赏、演奏、即兴创作、乐队合奏的立体化创意课程，使学生敏于审美，敢于表达，精于创造，乐于合作，真正享受音乐的乐趣。</span></p><p style="color: inherit; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;" class="p2"><span style="font-size: 14px;">机构现设2个常规教学点（闸北教室、碧云教室）和3个合作教学点，环境一流，服务细致，师资雄厚。机构配备完整的教材和课程体系，并提供国内外标准化现代音乐考级培训（ROCKSCHOOL/英皇/迷笛），根据学生特点分阶训练，提供个性化教学。RM还首创线上智能教务系统，通过信息化管理辅助教学，学生可 以在线完成作业、查询课程信息、评价老师、获取RM音乐库歌曲和教学视频等，使学生-家长-机构零距离沟通，更好的实现高品质，高效率的教学模式。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;" class="p2"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;" class="p2"><span style="font-size: 14px;">RM区别于传统的教学理念，认为音乐带给孩子的应该是享受和成长，而非枯燥乏味的技巧重复。我们通过组建乐队教会孩子合作与社交，用即兴演奏挖掘孩子的潜能和想象力，指导孩子作词编曲开发创造力，带孩子体验不同音乐风格提升审美，让孩子在多元化的立体课程中真正学会享受音乐的乐趣。除日常教学外，RM会不定期组织学员参加各类演出活动，通过演出来激发学员的积极性，提高自信心与自我认同感，丰富学员的舞台经验和社会实践经验，给有意愿出国深造的同学提供丰富简历的便利条件。</span></p><p style="color: inherit; white-space: normal;"><br/></p></section></section><section style="margin: -8px 0px 0px -6px; padding: 3px; border-radius: 100%; width: 14px; height: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1; float: left; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"><section style="border-radius: 50%; width: 8px; height: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(33, 33, 34);"></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; box-sizing: border-box;" class="135editor" data-id="86449" data-tools="135编辑器"><section style="margin-top: 1em; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"><section style="text-align: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: 0.6em; font-size: 4em; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;"><em class="135brush" data-brushtype="text">A</em></section></section><section style="color: inherit; margin-left: 0.2em; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="line-height: 1.4; white-space: normal;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text">BOUT</p><p style="line-height: 1.4; font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text">Rolling Music</p></section></section><section style="color: inherit; margin-top: -1em; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: -5px; border-top-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); border-right-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 18px 10px 0px; padding: 6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(235, 235, 236);" class="135brush"><p style="white-space: normal;" class="p1"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Rolling Music (RM), anamalgamation of music education and music performance, is an institution that was formed by one of the domestic, large-scale music festival founders with a competent planning team of international musicians with abundant educational experience. This group of professionals are dedicated to teaching music through modern culture, music theory and development, music appreciation, performance, and improvisation. RM promotes a three-dimensional curriculum assembled with a student-sensitive focus on aesthetics, creative expression, and skill development to produce music both individually and as a band.</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;" class="p2"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;" class="p1"><span style="font-size: 14px;">We are currently located in 2 conventional teaching centers (Zhabei Classroom and Green City Classroom) and three co-teaching centers. We provide a first-class environment, meticulous service, and a dynamic teaching team. With textbooks and curriculum based upon the domestic and international standards of modern music (RockSchool/Letters/Midi). Students can train in phases with the option of individualized training. RM has created an online system to assist in managing classroom instruction. Course materials, such as Rolling Music’s song library, instruction videos, homework, and teacher evaluations, are compiled to establish efficient communication between students, parents, and teachers.</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;" class="p2"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;" class="p1"><span style="font-size: 14px;">RM attributes different methods from the traditional teaching philosophy . Children should enjoy learning theory and techniques of music as they develop their skills, rather than the average repetition. We also teach students the art of forming a band. The ability to cooperate with others in a social setting, tapping into the student expression and imagination, development of creativity, and appreciation of a variety of music genres compose the essence of RM presentation. In addition to music training, RM occasionally provides students with the opportunity to participate in public performances. We believe allowing students to present their skills and projects stimulates their enthusiasm, develops confidence and identity, and provides stage experience.&nbsp;</span></p><p style="color: inherit; white-space: normal;"><br/></p></section></section><section style="margin-top: -1.8em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: -8px 0px 0px -6px; padding: 3px; border-radius: 100%; width: 14px; height: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1; float: left; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"><section style="border-radius: 50%; width: 8px; height: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(33, 33, 34);"></section></section></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><section style="-webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);"></section></section><p><br/></p>', '关于Rolling Music', '', '/uploads/201608069698IeVa6BF3wZ.jpg', '', 'single', '2016-08-06 02:49:20');
